# MF Purchase Optimizer — Low Level Design (LLD) Block Diagram

> **Stack**: FastAPI (Python) · React + Vite · SQLite (SQLAlchemy ORM) · Docker

---

## 1. Overall System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Browser["🌐 Browser (React + Vite)"]
        FE["Frontend App\n(Port 3001 / 5173)"]
    end

    subgraph DockerCompose["🐳 Docker Compose"]
        FE_Container["NGINX\nfrontend:3001"]
        BE_Container["FastAPI\nbackend:8000"]
    end

    subgraph ExternalServices["☁️ External Services"]
        SMTP["SMTP Email\n(Gmail)"]
        MFAPI["mfapi.in\nNAV Data API"]
    end

    FE -->|HTTP /api/*| FE_Container
    FE_Container -->|Reverse Proxy /api/| BE_Container
    BE_Container -->|send emails| SMTP
    BE_Container -->|fetch NAV/fund metadata| MFAPI
    BE_Container -->|SQLite| DB[("mfpo.db\nSQLite Database")]
```

---

## 2. Frontend Component Tree

```mermaid
graph TD
    Main["main.jsx\nReact Root"]
    Main --> App["App.jsx\nRouter + Providers"]

    App --> AuthProv["AuthContext\n(JWT, user state)"]
    App --> ToastProv["ToastContext\n(Global Notifications)"]
    App --> ErrBound["ErrorBoundary"]

    App --> Routes["React Router\nRoutes"]

    Routes --> Home["/  →  Home.jsx"]
    Routes --> Signup["/signup  →  Signup.jsx"]
    Routes --> Signin["/signin  →  Signin.jsx"]
    Routes --> VerifyOTP["/verify-otp  →  VerifyOTP.jsx"]
    Routes --> LoginOTP["/login-otp  →  LoginOTP.jsx"]
    Routes --> ForgotPW["/forgot-password  →  ForgotPassword.jsx"]
    Routes --> ResetPW["/reset-password  →  ResetPassword.jsx"]

    Routes --> ProtClient["ProtectedRoute\n[investor]"]
    Routes --> ProtAdmin["ProtectedRoute\n[admin]"]
    Routes --> ProtAdvisor["ProtectedRoute\n[advisor]"]

    ProtClient --> CD["ClientDashboard.jsx"]
    ProtAdmin --> AD["AdminDashboard.jsx"]
    ProtAdvisor --> AdvD["AdvisorDashboard.jsx"]

    CD --> RM["RiskProfileModal.jsx"]
    CD --> ISM["InvestmentSuccessModal.jsx"]
    CD --> Portfolio["Portfolio.jsx"]
    CD --> IH["InvestmentHistory.jsx"]
    CD --> Profile["Profile.jsx"]
    CD --> SharedProf["SharedProfile.jsx"]

    AdvD --> SharedProf
```

