## 3. Frontend Service Layer

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Services["src/services/"]
        API["api.js\nAxios Instance\nbaseURL: /api"]
    end

    subgraph Context["src/context/"]
        AuthCtx["AuthContext.jsx\nlogin / logout / user"]
        ToastCtx["ToastContext.jsx\nshowToast()"]
        UseAuth["useAuth.js\nhook"]
    end

    API -->|Bearer JWT\nattached via interceptor| BackendAPI["FastAPI Backend\n/api/*"]
    API -->|401 → auto refresh\nor redirect /signin| AuthCtx
    AuthCtx --> UseAuth
    ToastCtx -->|triggers| Toast["Toast.jsx"]
```

